<p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">9月5日 ，江西软件职业技术大学2023级新生从五湖四海如约而至，他们满怀憧憬，为校园注入青春与活力，正式开启在江软的崭新旅程。各学院迎新站点、校园接驳车、缴费报到处有序接待远道而来的新生。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">智慧迎新</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">学校发挥软件企业办软件大学的特色优势，以“智慧”迎新。使用校园通系统和智慧校园平台，对新生数据进行大数据管理，优化助学贷款信息提交、贫困生专项补助等事务流程。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-06%2022%3A03%3A13IMG_0571.JPG?Expires=2009368993&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=%2BvS4BMJlPgfwQDppXnxa4QonV4A%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-08%2008%3A56%3A52%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20230908085445.jpg?Expires=2009494612&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=q8eF2zeRW%2FxtI%2B4wo3ImeIhrisU%3D" alt="" width="650" height="367" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">在迎新前一周，学校优化接站程序，以线上填写征集到站时间人数的方式，合理调配接站车辆、志愿者人数等人力物力，确保有序接站。同学们可以在网上完成前置教育课程学习、网上预交费等，简化学生报到流程。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-06%2022%3A03%3A56IMG_9260.JPG?Expires=2009369036&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=oUNgSksf7uLgQGzriGwmrIkWPwM%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">以“心”迎新</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">随处可见的工作人员和志愿者们为迎新工作忙碌不停，他们以真诚和热情欢迎新生到的到来，引导新生完成注册报到，耐心地为新生和新生家长解疑答惑。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">据悉，今年迎新工作有600余名师生志愿报名参加志愿服务。他们或是热情帮助新生搬运行李，或是主动上前提供服务指引，成为校园里最靓丽的风景线。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-06%2022%3A04%3A15IMG_0580.JPG?Expires=2009369055&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=NawWhXTabdj%2FDfoW5iuOzj%2BAktQ%3D" width="650" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-06%2022%3A28%3A59IMG_0579_wps%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87.JPG?Expires=2009370539&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=HE8uCsW5QK9d%2FX3tbTrHFUXgBV4%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">此外，学校还策划了形式多样的入学打卡点。各具特色的互动展板、定制的签名墙，让迎新氛围感拉满。各学院迎新点也有俏皮可爱的手持迎新板、清凉解渴的柠檬茶、酸甜解腻的话梅糖等暖心的细节，还有热情洋溢的公益活动，让新生与新生家长感受到江软校园如家般的温情和积极向上的青春气息。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-06%2022%3A27%3A011694010392%281%29.png?Expires=2009370421&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=w6Weg7UohYdk8qJldX3OaSFtvSM%3D" alt="" width="650" height="433" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-06%2022%3A27%3A311694010422%281%29.png?Expires=2009370451&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=at%2BQL0V%2Fl5Dx34YFLCnSVkzBFAk%3D" alt="" width="650" height="439" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">关怀迎新</span></strong></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">为了迎接新生到来，学校成立迎新工作小组，多次召开迎新工作部署会，从前期迎新工作准备，迎新氛围营造，到新生接站、报到、入住及入学教育等各方面均进行全方位的安排与部署，积极为同学们打造温馨、热情、周到的入学服务。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">迎新期间，校党委书记、督导专员江延湖，执行校长范红铭，常务副校长李旺根等校领导，在相关部门负责人的陪同下，全流程视察和指导迎新，看望慰问各学院、职能部门参加迎新的教职工、志愿者。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-07%2010%3A13%3A13IMG_9595.JPG?Expires=2009412793&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ku%2FJlubAmTjH58l4rZfwviZOpmI%3D" alt="" width="650" height="365" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2023-09-08%2008%3A57%3A17%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87_20230908085452.jpg?Expires=2009494637&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=VZvjMIrLZJJ01FQg4zbXNPH4Jbs%3D" alt="" width="650" height="367" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block;"/></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-